{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775885968013,"sessionID":"ses_284f4b12cffevFM0IiCANL0Nzt","part":{"id":"prt_d7b0d6223001mwpEiYgdzdCmOg","messageID":"msg_d7b0ba0ed001ACqNdYug0ETgqb","sessionID":"ses_284f4b12cffevFM0IiCANL0Nzt","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-e4e236ff02864f3ab753ac21568fdba2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-034 — CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows) Tasks\n\n**Module**: `.github`\n**Language**: `YAML`\n**Size**: `L`\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Create .github directory structure\n- [ ] Create .github/workflows/ directory if it doesn't exist\n- [ ] Create .github/actions/ directory for reusable actions\n- [ ] Create .github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/ directory for issue templates\n- [ ] Create .github/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE/ directory for PR templates\n- [ ] Verify directory permissions are correct\n- [ ] Add .github/ to .gitignore if not already present\n- [ ] Document directory structure in README.md\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ntest -d .github/workflows && echo \"workflows exists\" || echo \"workflows missing\"\ntest -d .github/actions && echo \"actions exists\" || echo \"actions missing\"\nls -la .github/\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- All required directories are created\n- Directory structure follows GitHub best practices\n- Documentation is updated\n\n---\n\n### Task 2: Create ci-pr-checks workflow\n- [ ] Create .github/workflows/ci-pr-checks.yml\n- [ ] Set workflow trigger on pull_request to main branch\n- [ ] Set workflow trigger on push to main branch\n- [ ] Add job matrix for Go and Python checks\n- [ ] Configure checkout action with fetch-depth: 0\n- [ ] Set up Go environment (version 1.21+)\n- [ ] Set up Python environment (version 3.11+)\n- [ ] Add job to run Go tests (make test-go)\n- [ ] Add job to run Python tests (make test-python)\n- [ ] Add job to run Go linting (make lint-go)\n- [ ] Add job to run Python linting (make lint-python)\n- [ ] Add job to check code formatting (make format-check)\n- [ ] Configure job dependencies (lint before tests)\n- [ ] Add artifact upload for test results\n- [ ] Add coverage report upload to Codecov\n- [ ] Configure job timeout (30 minutes)\n- [ ] Add job status checks required for PR merge\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ntest -f .github/workflows/ci-pr-checks.yml && echo \"workflow exists\" || echo \"workflow missing\"\nyamllint .github/workflows/ci-pr-checks.yml || echo \"YAML syntax valid\"\ngrep -q \"on: pull_request\" .github/workflows/ci-pr-checks.yml && echo \"PR trigger configured\" || echo \"PR trigger missing\"\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- Workflow file is syntactically valid YAML\n- Workflow triggers on PR and push to main\n- All check jobs are defined\n- Jobs have proper dependencies and timeouts\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: Create lint-checks workflow\n- [ ] Create .github/workflows/lint-checks.yml\n- [ ] Set workflow trigger on pull_request to all branches\n- [ ] Set workflow trigger on push to all branches\n- [ ] Add job for Go linting\n- [ ] Configure golangci-lint with .golangci.yml config\n- [ ] Add job for Python linting with ruff\n- [ ] Add job for Python type checking with mypy\n- [ ] Add job for YAML linting with yamllint\n- [ ] Add job for markdown linting with markdownlint\n- [ ] Add job for shell script linting with shellcheck\n- [ ] Configure caching for linter installations\n- [ ] Add job failure annotations\n- [ ] Configure job to run on ubuntu-latest\n- [ ] Set job timeout (15 minutes)\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ntest -f .github/workflows/lint-checks.yml && echo \"workflow exists\" || echo \"workflow missing\"\ngrep -q \"golangci-lint\" .github/workflows/lint-checks.yml && echo \"Go linting configured\" || echo \"Go linting missing\"\ngrep -q \"ruff\" .github/workflows/lint-checks.yml && echo \"Python linting configured\" || echo \"Python linting missing\"\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- All linting jobs are defined\n- Jobs run on appropriate events\n- Caching is configured\n- Failure annotations are enabled\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: Create unit-tests workflow\n- [ ] Create .github/workflows/unit-tests.yml\n- [ ] Set workflow trigger on pull_request and push\n- [ ] Add job matrix for Go tests (multiple Go versions)\n- [ ] Add job matrix for Python tests (multiple Python versions)\n- [ ] Configure Go test job with race detection\n- [ ] Configure Python test job with pytest\n- [ ] Add test coverage collection for Go\n- [ ] Add test coverage collection for Python\n- [ ] Upload coverage reports as artifacts\n- [ ] Upload coverage to Codecov\n- [ ] Add test result parsing for JUnit XML\n- [ ] Configure test timeout (20 minutes)\n- [ ] Add test retries on failure (max 2)\n- [ ] Add test summary to PR comments\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ntest -f .github/workflows/unit-tests.yml && echo \"workflow exists\" || echo \"workflow missing\"\ngrep -q \"race\" .github/workflows/unit-tests.yml && echo \"Race detection configured\" || echo \"Race detection missing\"\ngrep -q \"codecov\" .github/workflows/unit-tests.yml && echo \"Codecov configured\" || echo \"Codecov missing\"\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- Unit tests run for all supported versions\n- Coverage is collected and uploaded\n- Test results are parsed and displayed\n- Race detection is enabled\n\n---\n\n### Task 5: Create integration-tests workflow\n- [ ] Create .github/workflows/integration-tests.yml\n- [ ] Set workflow trigger on pull_request and push to main\n- [ ] Set workflow trigger on nightly schedule (cron: 0 2 * * *)\n- [ ] Add job for Go integration tests\n- [ ] Add job for Python integration tests\n- [ ] Add job for end-to-end tests\n- [ ] Set up required services (Docker compose)\n- [ ] Configure test environment with secrets\n- [ ] Add database setup and teardown\n- [ ] Configure test data fixtures\n- [ ] Add test isolation between tests\n- [ ] Configure test timeout (45 minutes)\n- [ ] Upload test logs as artifacts\n- [ ] Add test result summarization\n- [ ] Configure test failure notifications\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ntest -f .github/workflows/integration-tests.yml && echo \"workflow exists\" || echo \"workflow missing\"\ngrep -q \"cron:\" .github/workflows/integration-tests.yml && echo \"Schedule configured\" || echo \"Schedule missing\"\ngrep -q \"docker-compose\" .github/workflows/integration-tests.yml && echo \"Services configured\" || echo \"Services missing\"\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- Integration tests run on schedule and events\n- Services are properly set up and torn down\n- Tests are isolated and repeatable\n- Logs are collected on failure\n\n---\n\n### Task 6: Create build-docker workflow\n- [ ] Create .github/workflows/build-docker.yml\n- [ ] Set workflow trigger on pull_request and push to main\n- [ ] Set workflow trigger on release (types: [published])\n- [ ] Add job matrix for multiple platforms (linux/amd64, linux/arm64)\n- [ ] Configure Docker Buildx for multi-platform builds\n- [ ] Set up QEMU for cross-compilation\n- [ ] Add job to build agentd image\n- [ ] Add job to build picod image\n- [ ] Add job to build runtime image\n- [ ] Configure build arguments (VERSION, GIT_COMMIT, BUILD_TIME)\n- [ ] Cache Docker layers for faster builds\n- [ ] Run security scan with Trivy\n- [ ] Scan for HIGH and CRITICAL vulnerabilities\n- [ ] Upload scan results as artifacts\n- [ ] Configure job timeout (60 minutes)\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ntest -f .github/workflows/build-docker.yml && echo \"workflow exists\" || echo \"workflow missing\"\ngrep -q \"buildx\" .github/workflows/build-docker.yml && echo \"Buildx configured\" || echo \"Buildx missing\"\ngrep -q \"trivy\" .github/workflows/build-docker.yml && echo \"Security scan configured\" || echo \"Security scan missing\"\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- Docker images build for multiple platforms\n- Buildx and QEMU are configured\n- Security scanning is enabled\n- Build caching is configured\n\n---\n\n### Task 7: Create security-scan workflow\n- [ ] Create .github/workflows/security-scan.yml\n- [ ] Set workflow trigger on pull_request and push to main\n- [ ] Set workflow trigger on schedule (cron: 0 6 * * 0)\n- [ ] Add job for Go dependency vulnerability scan\n- [ ] Use govulncheck for Go vulnerabilities\n- [ ] Add job for Python dependency vulnerability scan\n- [ ] Use pip-audit for Python vulnerabilities\n- [ ] Add job for Docker image security scan\n- [ ] Use Trivy for container scanning\n- [ ] Add job for code security analysis\n- [ ] Use CodeQL for security queries\n- [ ] Configure severity thresholds (HIGH, CRITICAL)\n- [ ] Upload scan results as SARIF files\n- [ ] Upload results to GitHub Security tab\n- [ ] Configure failure on HIGH/CRITICAL findings\n- [ ] Add security scan summary to PR comments\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ntest -f .github/workflows/security-scan.yml && echo \"workflow exists\" || echo \"workflow missing\"\ngrep -q \"govulncheck\" .github/workflows/security-scan.yml && echo \"Go vuln scan configured\" || echo \"Go vuln scan missing\"\ngrep -q \"codeql\" .github/workflows/security-scan.yml && echo \"CodeQL configured\" || echo \"CodeQL missing\"\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- All security scans are configured\n- Scans run on schedule and events\n- Results are uploaded to GitHub Security\n- Failures occur on HIGH/CRITICAL findings\n\n---\n\n### Task 8: Create release workflow\n- [ ] Create .github/workflows/release.yml\n- [ ] Set workflow trigger on release (types: [published])\n- [ ] Add job to validate release tag format\n- [ ] Add job to build all binaries\n- [ ] Add job to build Docker images\n- [ ] Add job to build Python packages\n- [ ] Configure release artifact generation\n- [ ] Generate checksums for all artifacts\n- [ ] Upload binaries to release assets\n- [ ] Upload Docker images to registry\n- [ ] Upload Python packages to PyPI\n- [ ] Generate release notes from commits\n- [ ] Add changelog to release description\n- [ ] Configure registry credentials as secrets\n- [ ] Configure PyPI credentials as secrets\n- [ ] Configure job timeout (60 minutes)\n- [ ] Add release notification (Slack/email)\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ntest -f .github/workflows/release.yml && echo \"workflow exists\" || echo \"workflow missing\"\ngrep -q \"types: \\[published\\]\" .github/workflows/release.yml && echo \"Release trigger configured\" || echo \"Release trigger missing\"\ngrep -q \"PyPI\" .github/workflows/release.yml && echo \"PyPI configured\" || echo \"PyPI missing\"\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- Workflow triggers on release publication\n- All artifacts are built and uploaded\n- Release notes are generated automatically\n- Credentials are configured as secrets\n\n---\n\n### Task 9: Create deploy-staging workflow\n- [ ] Create .github/workflows/deploy-staging.yml\n- [ ] Set workflow trigger on manual workflow_dispatch\n- [ ] Set workflow trigger on push to develop branch\n- [ ] Add job to build and test artifacts\n- [ ] Add job to deploy to staging environment\n- [ ] Configure deployment strategy (rolling or blue-green)\n- [ ] Configure staging environment secrets\n- [ ] Add health check verification\n- [ ] Add rollback capability on failure\n- [ ] Configure deployment timeout (30 minutes)\n- [ ] Add deployment notifications\n- [ ] Add deployment status badge\n- [ ] Configure environment protection rules\n- [ ] Add deployment approval requirement\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ntest -f .github/workflows/deploy-staging.yml && echo \"workflow exists\" || echo \"workflow missing\"\ngrep -q \"workflow_dispatch\" .github/workflows/deploy-staging.yml && echo \"Manual trigger configured\" || echo \"Manual trigger missing\"\ngrep -q \"health\" .github/workflows/deploy-staging.yml && echo \"Health check configured\" || echo \"Health check missing\"\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- Workflow can be triggered manually or automatically\n- Deployment to staging is configured\n- Health checks and rollback are enabled\n- Approval requirements